# Keep the directory tracked; drop in-flight + editor junk. Committed
# reports live under per-release subdirectories (v0.1.0/, v0.1.1/, ...).
# The top-level *.json files are transient: each `cargo bench` invocation
# rewrites the one for the current sha, and check-release.sh copies the
# approved run into the version subdir. Ignoring them here prevents
# accidental commits of CI-workstation transients.
*.tmp
*.swp
/*.json
